metadata.name: Guardians
metadata.description:
Guardians is a Symbolic Visualisation Guide for the Balancing & Purification Meditation of Ida & Pingala: The Divine Subtle Energy Streams that spiral around The Central Pranic Nadi 'Sushumna' & Guard the Indigo Crystal of Sahasrara: Gateway to The Pineal Rainbow Bridge, Secret Key to The Awakening & Energetic Harmonisation of Kundalini Shakti, Temple of The Sacred Alchemical Union.

Edition: 1/1, 2.2k, 1min AV seamless loop.
Collector will receive an exclusive uncompressed 4k version.
